<GORGINES CACISTVS ASPASIVS>

Gorg. animum aduortite ambō sultis. uidulum hic apponite.
ego seruabō, quasī sequestrō detis. neutrī reddibō,
donicum rēs iudicata erit haec.
Asp. Haud fugiō sequestrum
